Hi everyone!
Has any of you applied for UI when the COVID19 hit? Did you receive any response? It's been 2 weeks for me and I still haven't gotten response from them. All I have is the confirmation number.
Do you know if there's a way we can maybe check the status online or somehow get a hold of someone there?

Feel free to ask or leave your comment here for others here regarding EDD/COVID19.
